## Choose your operating environment

Next, choose where you'll manage your Red Hat Enterprise Linux or CentOS server. All options provide similar content, but each is tailored to most closely match where you run your servers.

The [free virtual machine](/tutorials/learn-the-basics/rhel/free/) option is the easiest way to get started.

